{
  "chapter": {
    "title": "Honnoji",
    "subtitle": "1582 \u2014 Every ending was always this one.",
    "chapterOrder": 8,
    "isLocked": false
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneRef": "S01",
      "backgroundKey": "honnoji_temple_night_arrival",
      "bgmKey": "bgm_ominous",
      "sceneOrder": 1,
      "nextSceneRef": "S02",
      "isBattleGate": false,
      "isChapterEnd": false,
      "dialogueLines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "June, 1582. Honnoji temple in Kyoto. Nobunaga travels with a small escort \u2014 thirty men. He is resting here before the western campaign, which he expects to resolve Japan inside of two years.",
          "lineOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "The temple is quiet. The city is asleep. Mitsuhide is in the west, commanding the advance force. He is three days away.",
          "lineOrder": 2
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "Except that he is not.",
          "lineOrder": 3
        }
      ],
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "_comment": "resolveConditionalScene candidates for the S02 slot, ordered: S02_LOYAL (mitsuhide_loyalty >= 2) → S02_COLD (mitsuhide_loyalty <= 0) → S02 (unconditional fallback). The unconditional fallback covers the mid-range player.",
      "sceneRef": "S02_LOYAL",
      "backgroundKey": "honnoji_temple_courtyard_torches",
      "bgmKey": "bgm_war_drums",
      "sceneOrder": 2,
      "nextSceneRef": "S03",
      "isBattleGate": false,
      "isChapterEnd": false,
      "flagCondition": {
        "flagKey": "mitsuhide_loyalty",
        "operator": "gte",
        "value": 2
      },
      "dialogueLines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "My lord \u2014 torches. The outer wall. Thousands of them.",
          "lineOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "Whose banner?",
          "lineOrder": 2
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "...",
          "lineOrder": 3
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "Akechi, my lord.",
          "lineOrder": 4
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "Akechi Mitsuhide. His most capable general. His longest-serving advisor. The man he asked, in the map room years ago, to tell him if he was treating people as tools.",
          "lineOrder": 5
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "...Mitsuhide.",
          "lineOrder": 6
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "He says only the name. It takes a moment \u2014 personal before tactical, weight before calculation. Then:",
          "lineOrder": 7
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "Is this the realm, then. \u2026 It cannot be helped.",
          "lineOrder": 8
        }
      ],
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "sceneRef": "S02_COLD",
      "backgroundKey": "honnoji_temple_courtyard_torches",
      "bgmKey": "bgm_war_drums",
      "sceneOrder": 3,
      "nextSceneRef": "S03",
      "isBattleGate": false,
      "isChapterEnd": false,
      "flagCondition": {
        "flagKey": "mitsuhide_loyalty",
        "operator": "lte",
        "value": 0
      },
      "dialogueLines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "My lord \u2014 torches. The outer wall. Thousands of them.",
          "lineOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "Whose banner?",
          "lineOrder": 2
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "Akechi, my lord.",
          "lineOrder": 3
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "How many?",
          "lineOrder": 4
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Ranmaru",
          "speakerSide": "left",
          "portraitKey": "ranmaru_panicked",
          "text": "Thirteen thousand, my lord.",
          "lineOrder": 5
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Narrator",
          "speakerSide": "none",
          "portraitKey": null,
          "text": "Nobunaga nods. No surprise at the name. No pause before the number. The tool reached its tolerance and broke, as tools do. He had known, somewhere, that it would come to this.",
          "lineOrder": 6
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "Nobunaga",
          "speakerSide": "right",
          "portraitKey": "nobunaga_cold",
          "text": "It cannot be helped.",
          "lineOrder": 7
        }
      ],
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "sceneRef": "S02",
      "backgroundKey": "honnoji_temple_courtyard_torches",
      "bgmKey": "bgm_war_drums",
      "sceneOrder": 4,
      "nextSceneRef": "S03",
